'''Black Dust Industries''' was a holding company owned by the retired [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] [[Karl Mathieu Ancher]] on [[Socorro/Legends|Socorro]]. The coalition held shares in the [[Black Dust Tavern]], [[Boliscon Towers]], and [[Ethra Brewery]]. In addition to these holdings, Black Dust Industries owned massive shares of land on [[Neftali/Legends|Neftali]] and settlement donations from the [[Black Bha'lir]]. An association of legitimate businesses, Black Dust Industries was somewhat of a minority on Socorro.

